Find the right class to start your freediving training.

We offer classes for all levels and ages. Find the right fit below.

  • swimming lessons

    $200-$400

    Learn to Swim! Ages 18 months and up! Package includes 10 private lessons. For ages 3+, each lesson is 30 minutes. For ages 18-36 months, each lesson is 15 minutes.

    Learn more

  • little divers

    $300

    Kids age 5-15 learn to equalize, dive, hold their breath longer and become more confident and safe in the water.

    Includes six, one hour classes

    learn more

  • molchanovs wave 1 (beginner)

    $550

    For ages 16+, you will learn all the essential skills and technique needed to become a certified Freediver. Includes dry training, theory workshops and open water sessions.

    Includes twenty hours of training

    Learn more

  • molchanovs wave 2 (advanced)

    $550

    For certified wave 1 freedivers (or crossovers), take your skills to the next level by mastering free-fall, and extend limits on all disciplines.

    Includes twenty hours of training

    learn more
Best dive instructor we’ve ever had! So patient and kind, easy to work with. My girls are both equalizing, rock running and diving deeper than they ever have. They even use their pre dive mantra “calm heart, deep breath” when practicing I the bath tub. Diving in the ocean has made them more confident swimmers and overall more calm and balanced little humans. Could not recommend more!
